#: ../source/tutorial/configure-x509-client-authentication.txt:127
msgid ""
"The RDNs in the ``subject`` string must be compatible with the `RFC2253 "
"<https://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2253.txt>`_ standard."
msgstr ""

